<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span> صحيح ـ انظر <span class="c2">(١١٢٧)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبُو حَاتِمٍ:</span> الصَّوْر: مُجْتَمِعُ النَّخْلِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>